Rowshaid Pellum, a 24-year-old Cerritos resident, and Long Beach residents 18-year-old Markeisha Williams, 19-year-old Shyteice Miles, and 23-year-old Santeea Ralph were all arrested and booked for alleged assault with a deadly weapon, conspiracy and defrauding an innkeeper.

All were booked at an Orange County jail and held in lieu of $25,000 bail. They were expected to appear in court on Tuesday, reports KTLA5.

